    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open the door to a world where demons whisper from beneath the glow of the screens.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A compact adventure game inspired by Japanese adventure classics like Snatcher, Policenauts and The Silver Case. Join retired Digital Exorcist Sawyer and his trusty sidekick Tomo as they investigate chilling crime scenes. Use your wit to guide conversations and help Sawyer rediscover his old techniques to solve the mysteries lurking throughout your adventure.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate Gruesome Crime Scenes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thoroughly explore crime scenes with your trusty computerized companion, Tomodachi, as you collect evidence and equipment to assist in your investigation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/86590abf37a8fcb4ea5f089d6ce420be.poster.avif?t=1752107313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/86590abf37a8fcb4ea5f089d6ce420be.webm?t=1752107313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/86590abf37a8fcb4ea5f089d6ce420be.mp4?t=1752107313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Purge like it’s 1999!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go head-to-head with demons, and use items and weapons you find to fend them off!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/7eaf9c0bf0b5d2c1264787615461506d.poster.avif?t=1752107313\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/7eaf9c0bf0b5d2c1264787615461506d.webm?t=1752107313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/7eaf9c0bf0b5d2c1264787615461506d.mp4?t=1752107313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Elevated Experience with Stylized Art Style and Soundtrack</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive, dark and gruesome setting. Brought to life through charming pixel art and a boppin’ soundtrack produced with classic digital synthesizers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/ace236a395e52d23cf27b968749a0c75.poster.avif?t=1752107313\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/ace236a395e52d23cf27b968749a0c75.webm?t=1752107313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299040/extras/ace236a395e52d23cf27b968749a0c75.mp4?t=1752107313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
